    <body>
        <div class="noteOkta">
            <p class="noteContent">Changes to the RADIUS Agent <span class="filepath">config.properties</span> are only loaded on agent restart. Always restart your agent after changing <span class="filepath">config.properties</span>. </p>
        </div>
        <ol>
            <li>Open the folder where the Okta RADIUS agent resides. The default installation folder is <span class="filepath">C:\Program Files (x86)\Okta\Okta RADIUS Agent\</span></li>
            <li>Open <span class="filepath">current\user\config\radius\config.properties</span>. Before making changes, create a backup of this file.</li>
            <li>Configure the  properties, as required.
                <MadCap:snippetBlock src="radius.agent.properties.flsnp" /></li>
            <li>Save the file. </li>
            <li>Any changes are effective after restarting the Okta RADIUS Agent service using the available Windows administrative tools.</li>
        </ol>
    </body>
</html>